Steps to Run the grow-pool script:-

1)  First  Run the setup.sh script

	Usage to run setup.sh is

	$ ./setup.sh  $diskname 
	
	( eg . suppose disk name is sdb1 then  run  $setup.sh  sdb1 )


2) Second run the grow_pool_001_pos.ksh  script

	$ ./grow_pool_001_pos.ksh   $second_diskname  

	( eg . suppose disk name is sdc1 then   $ ./grow_pool_001_pos.ksh  sdc1

3) Lastly run the cleanup.sh  script

	$ ./cleanup.sh 


Note :- This test case is tested on two disks (each of size 2GB).
